==English==
===Noun===
'''inch''' (''plural'' '''inches''')

# A unit of [[length]] equal to one-twelfth of a [[foot]] and equivalent to exactly 2.54 [[centimetre]]s.
# (''figurative'') An unspecified but very short distance.  ("Don't move an ''inch''!")

